REAL ESTATE INTELLIGENCE PLATFORM - CORE MEMORY & CONTEXT
====================================================================
Last Updated: 2026-05-02

## Real Estate Intelligence Platform — Use Case
This system is a **fraud detection and market intelligence platform** for the Maharashtra real estate market, built specifically to monitor RERA-registered projects and 99acres listings in cities like Akola, Amravati, and Nagpur.

### Core Problem It Solves
Maharashtra's real estate market has significant buyer risk — developers collecting money, letting RERA registrations lapse, filing false unit counts, or operating shell companies across multiple registrations. Buyers, journalists, regulators, and investors currently have no easy way to correlate signals across data sources.

### What It Actually Does

**Data Collection**
- Scrapes live property listings from 99acres (prices, localities, listing types)
- Scrapes MahaRERA's public portal for all registered projects (status, promoter details, complaints, financials)
- Enriches RERA records via MahaRERA's internal API (units sold, amount collected, completion dates, geocoordinates)

**Automated Fraud & Risk Detection**
- Flags promoters with repeated RERA complaints across multiple projects
- Detects escrow deficits (collected funds not properly held)
- Identifies stalled/lapsed projects by repeat offenders
- Cross-references RERA-flagged promoters against active 99acres listings (illegal selling without valid registration)
- Detects shell company clusters via promoter name similarity analysis
- Spots listing price outliers and locality-level price spikes

**Market Intelligence**
- Tracks daily price-per-sqft snapshots by locality and property type
- Detects statistically significant price trend spikes (7/14/30-day windows)
- Computes confidence scores (0–100) on every flag based on data quality and corroboration

**Alerting**
- Pushes high-confidence flags (score ≥ 60, severity high/critical) to a Make.com automation scenario for real-time alerts

### Who Would Use This
| User                      | Purpose                                                        |
|---------------------------|----------------------------------------------------------------|
| Home buyers               | Check if a project/promoter is flagged before investing        |
| Journalists / RTI activists | Identify fraud patterns across promoters                     |
| RERA regulators           | Prioritize enforcement using confidence-scored flags           |
| Real estate investors     | Spot price manipulation or distressed locality signals         |
| Banks / NBFCs             | Due diligence on project loan applications                     |

