1. Run `--score` for all 3 cities. Check `locality_price_spike` confidence output.
   If avg still below 50, raise `PRICE_LOCALITY_SPIKE_PCT` 0.40 → 0.60 and rerun `--patterns --score`.
2. Add confirmed/dismissed flag actions to dashboard (thumbs up/down per flag).
3. Let daily pipeline run passively for 30 more days.
4. Then start Pune RERA-only scrape.

